@node "Introduction" "Introduction"

@{b}Introduction@{ub}



Gallerius is an easy HTML gallery generator.
It was made because there wasn't easy and free software for that on MorphOS.
I hope you'll like it.
This version was been rewriten almost from scratch (thx Phibrizzo).


@endnode

@node "instalacja" "Installation"

@{b}Installation@{ub}


Unpack archive where do you want. Gallerius do not need any extra actions. ;)

@endnode

@node "wymagania" "Requirments"

@{b}Requirments:@{ub}


MorphOS 1.4+, a lot of photos :) and a fell like doing gallery.

@endnode

@node "usage" "Usage"

@{b}it's simple...@{ub}

@{b}Main Page:@{ub}

Source:
Select source directory with your pictures

Destination:
Select destination directory whitch include html file name, subdirectories
with pictures and previews.

@{b}Files:@{ub}
When user select source list, then he can select what files should be
added to our gallery here.

@{b}HTML page:@{ub}
This page contains settings for HTML file.
Here you can setup background, text, link and visited link colours and how
many pictures there will be in one row (how many columns). You can also setup
previews with file name or without it.

@{b}Output page:@{ub}
Here you can setup size of your previews and pictures. You can use other
than .jpeg file but they will be saved as .jpeg. 
You can also select scale mode here.

If you have already done everything make up the site name and click generate
button


@endnode

